Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:09.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:20.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:38.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:53.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:59.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:06.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:20.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:28.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:33.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be too\Ndangerous to sit back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:35.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and do nothing about\Nthat mobile air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:40.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are hereby sending the Chor\NTempest on a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis shall serve\Nas the relay point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if we discover the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That will be left to\Nyour discretion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do believe you have the capacity\Nto blow it up at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why do you think they\Ntook you off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's something that I\Ncan't quite put my finger on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:17.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:35.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,As if Sibylla Aer would\Never do as she's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:49.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you really\Ngoing to let this go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this makes me wonder\Nwhat the sibyllae are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:59.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I would give for that\Nkind of single-minded passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning\Nof that Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe it's Sibylla\NAer and Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:21.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer and Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:38.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,After Chor Rubor was\Ndisbanded, these two sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...were assigned to the\NMessis as your replacements...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and have been on\Nreconnaissance duty ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:49.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all that we have\Nto offer at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We heard about Dominüra and Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:56.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,But where are Aer and Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two will be\Nsitting out this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,There'll be plenty of\Ntime to discuss that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, won't you\Nplease come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should go over the\Ndetails of our mission, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like\Nyou to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a little early,\Nbut I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you in the\Ndining room in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll be along soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Roatre!\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you were\Ntaking so long, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:47.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your braids are\Nstarting to come undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll fix them for you.\NWe still have time anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those Simouns we\Nsaw at the Ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,...do you think they've made it\Nback to the highlands' base station?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're paired up with Morinas,\Nand she's an excellent auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,And even if something\Nshould go wrong somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'll be there to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:37.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is just a reconnaissance\Nmission after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:45.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be better if we could avoid\Ngoing into battle at all, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be the\Nbest of all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the data these two\Nhave gathered on patrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we've narrowed down the Shoukoku\Nair base's approximate location...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to this region right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,In those defenseless Similes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, we two will\Nhold the rearguard position...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and relay all\Ncommunications from the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no getting around the fact\Nthat the gap between the Similes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the Simouns in terms\Nof mobility is far too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Putting together a mixed unit like\Nthis... It's just not feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,There you go making rash\Npromises again, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you knock it off?\NBoth of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Alty's the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's try to get along, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:40.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're comrades. We all\Nate from the same pot, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, don't mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please continue, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, we'll have the\Nmembers of Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That Mamina's changed, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way, what did you\Nnot want her to say, Roatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,The mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knew Vura was flying\Nreconnaissance in a Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, and to make sure their\Nefforts don't go to waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the rest of us need to be\Nin top form during this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, this is where\Nwe're supposed to deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to proceed\Naccording to plan. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:37.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can the center deploy\NChor Tempest in this state?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:54.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just as Sibylla\NDominüra said to me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:57.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The center understands nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will be a while before\NChor Tempest returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like you both to get\Nsome rest while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:10.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's part of our duty\Nto rest... correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's correct, Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't miss any\Nsigns of Chor Tempest's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to reiterate\Nthat to the patrol unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,They forbade you from attending\NAnglas's funeral, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is rather harsh of our\Ncountry, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more tenuous a state\Nthey find themselves in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the more people try to cling to\Nthe comfort of their conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:45.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, I can see that\Nyou've changed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I'm detaching the cables for\Nthe time being." So she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,How annoying is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,So they must be having a private\Nconversation one adult to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:04.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I say leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,3 o'clock! There's a huge shadow\Nin that break in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep the\Ncommunication cables intact...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and approach from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we've found the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those Simouns we encountered\Nat the Ruins could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:37.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's just confirm that\Nbefore we head home, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:46.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's a chance that the enemy\Ncould be patrolling this area too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:33.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we go much farther, we'll be\Nleaving the patrol area, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we\Nshould be heading back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to our rendezvous\Npoint with the regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's patrol this\Narea a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:51.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,There it is! The Messis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the rear of our ship.\NA single Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Approaching at a rapid pace.\NIt's a Chor Tempest Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Aer and Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought we'd\Nfind Vura on board the Messis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's quite surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was worried\Nabout that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer and Sibylla\NYun, please go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought they might show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's head that way ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Channel all power from the\Nhelical motors to the engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're heading for the\Npatrol zone at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're heading toward the\Nrendezvous point with the regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, they've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Retreat at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:20.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:24.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shark Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger! Shark Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't shake them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those guys are way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,She just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril just told us\Nto make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should do as she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, both our\NSimouns will be shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry back\Nand let the others know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. We'll come\Nback for you as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:40.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can understand what I'm\Nsaying, then listen to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing but\Nan unknown sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...doomed to die in\Nsuch a place as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do I care\Nabout my own life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:19.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Behind me lies the finest sibylla\Nin all of Simulacrum Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting her out\Nof here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:28.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And not one of you will lay\Nso much as a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Both the sibylla behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you yourself are\Nthe finest of all sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You two are sibyllae\Nfrom Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no one closer\Nto God than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,In our nation,\Nthe Plumbum highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you are respected\Nabove all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is not our choice to\Nengage in battle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is not our will to\Ncapture an injured sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:04.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses of\Nthe Plumbum Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're not the same as the Shoukoku\Nsoldiers on board this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:12.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The battle we have just\Nbeen waging is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no longer any\Nreason for us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, you must believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we were planning\Nto capture you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then there would be no need\Nfor us to go to all these lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What those priestesses\Nare telling us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am sure it is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, you must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come, together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose!\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's what's\Ngoing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you four let us get\Naway from this base...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you'll have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:32.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. If they capture you,\Nyou are certain to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:45.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You four recognized\Nme as a true sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if you let me escape, you'll\Nbe put to death as traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:34.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're planning to go to your\Ndeath at the hands of those soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me say it in your language...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've sighted a huge\Nshadow straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, we believe it's\NShoukoku's aerial base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it appears to be on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, take your\Npositions for battle level one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, take your\Npositions for battle level one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace\Nyourself for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace\Nyourself for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're going\Nto the priestesses' aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back\Nto the Messis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:39.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:40.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,No!\NStep back, Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:41.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're in our way!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry too, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:51.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to get away from\Nhere! We've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:22:00.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to just stand\Nhere forever, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:26.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:59.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:06.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:32.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:44.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:53.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:59.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:06.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:06.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NShe was a proud sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:07.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a proud sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:10.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...not to mention just a young\Ngirl from Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now Sibylla Mamina is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lament
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lament\NLament.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:19.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lament
